        ) </span>

  </h2>


    <div id="db-doulist-section" class="indent">
      <ul class="bs">
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/1383824/" target="_blank">国学古籍：保留传统文化精髓</a>
                <span class="pl">(华东师范大学出版社)</span>
            </li>
          <li class=""><a class="" href="https://www.douban.com/doulist/142062/" target="_blank">庄子研究</a>
